ction_4-3\"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-Huffington_on_2010_reintroduction_4-4\"><sup><i><b>e</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Bohn, Lauren (July 3, 2010). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2010/05/03/workplace-religious-freed_n_561560.html\">\"Workplace Religious Freedom Bill Finds Revived Interest\"</a>. <i>The Huffington Post / Religious News Service</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">15 December</span> 2013</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Huffington+Post+%2F+Religious+News+Service&amp;rft.atitle=Workplace+Religious+Freedom+Bill+Finds+Revived+Interest&amp;rft.date=2010-07-03&amp;rft.aulast=Bohn&amp;rft.aufirst=Lauren&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffingtonpost.com%2F2010%2F05%2F03%2Fworkplace-religious-freed_n_561560.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AWorkplace+Religious+Freedom+Act\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-1999_version_-_Senate_-_Overview-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-1999_version_-_Senate_-_Overview_5-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.govtrack.us/congress/bills/106/s1668\">\"S. 1668 (106th): Workplace Religious Freedom Act of 1999\"</a>. GovTrack<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">15 December</span> 2013</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=S.+1668+%28106th%29%3A+Workplace+Religious+Freedom+Act+of+1999&amp;rft.pub=GovTrack&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govtrack.us%2Fcongress%2Fbills%2F106%2Fs1668&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AWorkplace+Religious+Freedom+Act\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2002_Version_-_Senate_-_Overview-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-2002_Version_-_Senate_-_Overview_6-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.govtrack.us/congress/bills/107/s2572\">\"S. 2572 (107th): Workplace Religious Freedom Act of 2002\"</a>. GovTrack<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">15 December</span> 2013</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=S.+2572+%28107th%29%3A+Workplace+Religious+Freedom+Act+of+2002&amp;rft.pub=GovTrack&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govtrack.us%2Fcongress%2Fbills%2F107%2Fs2572&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AWorkplace+Religious+Freedom+Act\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2003_version_-_Senate_-_overview-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-2003_version_-_Senate_-_overview_7-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.govtrack.us/congress/bills/108/s893\">\"S. 893 (108th): Workplace Religious Freedom Act of 2003\"</a>. GovTrack<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">15 December</span> 2013</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=S.+893+%28108th%29%3A+Workplace+Religious+Freedom+Act+of+2003&amp;rft.pub=GovTrack&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govtrack.us%2Fcongress%2Fbills%2F108%2Fs893&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AWorkplace+Religious+Freedom+Act\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</spa